He's out pretty cold right now.

01:15:30.092 --> 01:15:31.492
- What's wrong with him?

01:15:33.562 --> 01:15:35.296
- Pneumonia.

01:15:35.298 --> 01:15:39.467
But it's very common in
these neuromuscular cases.

