- Hey.

01:17:07.089 --> 01:17:09.123
- What are you doing here?

01:17:09.125 --> 01:17:11.492
- I'm here with Doug.

01:17:13.295 --> 01:17:15.529
Is that your friend?

01:17:20.569 --> 01:17:22.470
- Yeah.

